{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/complaints-procedure","content_id":"5f559714-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"We treat any written or spoken expression of dissatisfaction with the service provided by the headquarters of the Ministry of Justice or its staff as a complaint.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>If you have a complaint please contact:</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\nMinisterial Correspondence Unit<br>Ministry of Justice<br>102 Petty France<br>London<br>SW1H 9AJ<br>DX 152380 Westminster 8\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>We aim to reply to all complaints within 20 working days. If we cannot resolve your complaint we will tell you what steps you can take if you want your complaint to be further investigated.</p>\n\n<p>We only deal with complaints relating to the service provided by the headquarters of the Ministry of Justice and its staff.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2013-04-04T15:25:47Z"}],"organisation":"dcc907d6-433c-42df-9ffb-d9c68be5dc4d","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"complaints_procedure","first_published_at":"2013-04-04T17:25:47+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/complaints-procedure.cy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/complaints-procedure.cy","base_path":"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/complaints-procedure.cy","content_id":"5f559714-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"complaints_procedure","links":{},"locale":"cy","public_updated_at":"2013-04-04T15:25:47Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Gweithdrefn gwyno","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/complaints-procedure.cy","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisa